			Valid values for encryption-type are: Plain, Base64
			Default value: Plain
</description>
        <from>password</from>
        <to>password</to>
      </input>
      <input global="false" required="false">
        <description>[Conditional]: specified only when password parameter is mentioned and its a required when dynamic targeting
You can encrypt the password by specifying the encryption type .
Valid values:  Base64,Plain.
Note : should be specified when password is provided</description>
        <from>encryption-type</from>
        <to>encryption-type</to>
      </input>
      <input global="false" required="false">
